The download should have begun, you must stay logged in as anonymous for it to
complete. Once complete, you may log out and restart this Install Wizard.
It is safe to exit this Install Wizard for the time being.

Attention: you will be unable to use your main account during the download,
however you may stop it, log out, and restart it later from this Install Wizard.

Troubleshooting: If the download has not begun and Steam is showing you the
store, you forgot to log out of your main account, restart the Install Wizard
and make sure to log out of Steam before launching the download.
